ZH: 我的手下都是很优秀的员工。
EN: My subordinates are all excellent employees.

ZH: 他对手下非常严厉，却非常公正。
EN: He is very strict with his subordinates, but also very fair.

ZH: 这位警官手下的人都非常忠诚。
EN: The people under this police officer are all very loyal.

ZH: 我的手下任务完成得非常出色。
EN: My subordinates have done an excellent job completing the tasks.

ZH: 他手下的团队合作得非常默契。
EN: The team under him works together very well.

ZH: 手下的员工需要服从领导的指示。
EN: Subordinates need to obey the instructions of their superiors.

ZH: 这位总裁很信任他的手下。
EN: The CEO trusts his subordinates a lot.

ZH: 在这个公司，手下对领导的话非常听从。
EN: In this company, subordinates listen to their leaders very obediently.

ZH: 他的手下经验丰富，很有能力解决问题。
EN: His subordinates are experienced and capable of solving problems.

ZH: 经理每周与手下举行例会讨论工作进展。
EN: The manager holds regular meetings with his subordinates to discuss work progress.

ZH: 他的手下每天都为了完成任务而努力工作。
EN: His subordinates work hard every day to accomplish their tasks.

ZH: 这个部门的手下都非常称职。
EN: The subordinates in this department are all very competent.

ZH: 领导需要与手下保持良好的沟通。
EN: Leaders need to maintain good communication with their subordinates.

ZH: 他手下的员工经常给他提供有价值的建议。
EN: The employees under him often provide him with valuable suggestions.

ZH: 忠诚的手下会为领导努力工作。
EN: Loyal subordinates will work hard for their leaders.

ZH: 手下的团队需要具备协作能力。
EN: The team of subordinates needs to have collaborative abilities.

ZH: 这个军队的手下非常有组织能力。
EN: The subordinates in this army are very well-organized.

ZH: 他手下的员工都是专家。
EN: The employees under him are all experts.

ZH: 这位经理对手下的工作管理得非常细致。
EN: This manager pays very detailed attention to managing the work of his subordinates.

ZH: 这个项目需要一个能力强的手下。
